metadata.name: The Crypto Stars #006 - Robin Hood
metadata.description: The Crypto Stars Collection is made up of 333 unique handcrafted pieces by 3D artist Pierre Benjamin, these mix satire, caricature and pastiche. It is a tribute to the most iconic, legendary and controversial women and men (whether real or fictitious) from Ancient history until Modern times across multiple artistic disciplines. It is about highlighting influential individuals who have made an impact in history.
